  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nAfter @truffle/hdwallet-provider@1.2.3, truffle migration does not work perfectly.\r\n \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nWhen migrating a simple box (I used [mine](https://www.github.com/miguelmartinezinf/hdw-metacoin-box/tree/main/)) does not work well... It seems making an `eth_call` instead an `eth_sendTransaction`.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ truffle migrate --reset --verbose-rpc\r\n\r\nCompiling your contracts...\r\n===========================\r\n✔ Fetching solc version list from solc-bin. Attempt #1\r\n✔ Downloading compiler. Attempt #1.\r\n> Everything is up to date, there is nothing to compile.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nStarting migrations...\r\n======================\r\n> Network name:    'development'\r\n> Network id:      2018\r\n> Block gas limit: 16234336 (0xf7b760)\r\n\r\n\r\n2_deploy.js\r\n===========\r\n\r\n   Replacing 'Simple'\r\n   ------------------\r\n   > {\r\n   >   \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n   >   \"method\": \"eth_call\",\r\n   >   \"params\": [\r\n   >     {\r\n   >       \"from\": \"0xfe3b557e8fb62b89f4916b721be55ceb828dbd73\",\r\n   >       \"gas\": \"0x6691b7\",\r\n   >       \"gasPrice\": \"0x4a817c800\",\r\n   >       \"data\": \"\",\r\n   >       \"chainId\": \"0x7e2\"\r\n   >     },\r\n   >     \"latest\"\r\n   >   ],\r\n   >   \"id\": 1616586757215\r\n   > }\r\n\r\nError:  *** Deployment Failed ***\r\n\r\n\"Simple\" -- Internal error.\r\n\r\n    at /home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/deployer/src/deployment.js:365:1\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (internal/process/task_queues.js:97:5)\r\n    at Migration._deploy (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/Migration.js:74:1)\r\n    at Migration._load (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/Migration.js:61:1)\r\n    at Migration.run (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/Migration.js:212:1)\r\n    at Object.runMigrations (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/index.js:150:1)\r\n    at Object.runFrom (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/index.js:110:1)\r\n    at Object.runAll (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/index.js:114:1)\r\n    at Object.run (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/migrate/index.js:79:1)\r\n    at runMigrations (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/core/lib/commands/migrate.js:263:1)\r\n    at Object.run (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/core/lib/commands/migrate.js:228:1)\r\n    at Command.run (/home/miki/.nvm/versions/node/v12.20.1/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/core/lib/command.js:136:1)\r\nTruffle v5.2.5 (core: 5.2.5)\r\nNode v12.20.1\r\n```",
