    "body": "Starting with 1.2.4 all transactions fail with \"Error: Invalid Signature\". Reverting to 1.2.3 solves the problem.\r\n\r\nSetup:\r\n- `ganache-cli@6.12.x` to fork the mainnet\r\n- `@truffle/hdwallet-provider` to sign transactions in tests - 1.2.3 is good, 1.2.4 onwards fails\r\n\r\nPossibly related to the switch from `ethereumjs-tx` to `@ethereumjs/tx` in 1.2.4 as @lolieatapple mentioned above.",
